---

---

<header class="header">
  <div class="header-inner">
    <!-- 顶部标签 -->
    <div class="tag-line">
      <span class="tag">
        <span class="tag-dot"></span>
        开源工具集
      </span>
      <span class="tag-separator">·</span>
      <span class="tag-text">为大学物理实验而生</span>
      <span class="tag-separator">·</span>
      <span class="tag-text">Developed by 五水</span>
    </div>


    <!-- 主标题区域 -->
    <div class="title-group">
      <h1 class="main-title">
        <span class="title-line">大物实验</span>
        <span class="title-line accent">工具站</span>
      </h1>
      <div class="title-decoration">
        <div class="deco-line"></div>
        <span class="deco-icon">⚛</span>
        <div class="deco-line"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 描述 -->
    <p class="subtitle">
      告别繁琐手算，专注实验本身。<br />
      提供<strong>数据处理</strong>与<strong>公式计算</strong>两大核心工具，<br class="mobile-hide" />
      覆盖均值、标准差、不确定度等常见需求。
    </p>

    <!-- 统计信息 -->
    <div class="stats-row">
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-number">2</span>
        <span class="stat-label">核心工具</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-divider"></div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-number">∞</span>
        <span class="stat-label">节省的时间</span>
      </div>
      <!-- <div class="stat-divider"></div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-number">0</span>
        <span class="stat-label">收费项目</span>
      </div> -->
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<style>
  .header {
    padding: 6rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .header-inner {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* 标签行 */
  .tag-line {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--c-text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .tag {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.35rem 0.85rem;
    background: var(--c-accent-blue-soft);
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15);
    border-radius: 100px;
    color: var(--c-accent-blue);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
  }

  .tag-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--c-accent-blue);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: pulse-dot 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse-dot {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    50% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(0.8); }
  }

  .tag-separator {
    color: var(--c-text-dim);
  }

  .tag-text {
    color: var(--c-text-muted);
  }

  /* 标题 */
  .title-group {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .main-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .title-line {
    display: block;
  }

  .title-line.accent {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--c-accent-blue), var(--c-accent-violet));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .title-decoration {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .deco-line {
    height: 1px;
    width: 60px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--c-border-hover), transparent);
  }

  .deco-icon {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  /* 描述 */
  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--c-text-muted);
    font-weight: 300;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
  }

  .subtitle strong {
    color: var(--c-text);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* 统计 */
  .stats-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    padding: 1.25rem 2rem;
    background: var(--c-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--c-border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    display: inline-flex;
  }

  .stat-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--c-text);
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--c-text-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .stat-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 32px;
    background: var(--c-border);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .header {
      padding: 4rem 1.25rem 3rem;
    }

    .mobile-hide {
      display: none;
    }

    .stats-row {
      gap: 1.25rem;
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .stat-number {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>